# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## Release 1.0.0

**Features**
- Migrated from bolt.yaml to bolt-project.yaml
- Renamed the boltello Puppet module to "boltello_builder" to avoid namespace collisions after the move to project-based Bolt
- Refactor boltello::add_nodes
- Refactor boltello::versionlock
- Ensure Foreman REX works across all katello nodes and new agent nodes
- Upgrade to Katello 3.17 rc1/Foreman 2.2
- Add postgresql 12.x support
- Refactor boltello::katello_upgrade and boltello::katello_prep
- Ensure smart-proxy TCPv4 connectivity by switching 'bind_host' property to '*'
- Update docs
**Bugfixes**
- Fix nginx reverse proxy $ssl_client_x_dn header variable: https://serverfault.com/questions/829754/why-did-the-format-of-nginx-ssl-client-i-dn-suddenly-change
**Known Issues**
